HEADWORD: first aid
<hw>first` aid"</hw> <pr>(f⟦etil⟧rst` ⟦amac⟧d")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Medical care provided immediately after an injury or sudden illness
for the purpose of minimizing injurious effects, before more complete
medical care becomes available.</def>⟦br⟧
